item_assets/steam/apps/2392900/extras/d99b2ec4467234cfde98e614b80f4071.mp4?t=1772214907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392900/extras/f6dbc83926655ea06bfe887bf1c48cfb.avif?t=1772214907\" width=618 height=110 /></span>您是否对制作自己的机械键盘望而生畏？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机械键盘制作模拟器》旨在让最缺乏经验的键盘爱好者也能轻松上手，它提供了按正确顺序组装部件的分步指导。了解每个部件及其用途的宝贵信息，并获得将梦想键盘变为现实的信心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392900/extras/eade8657f9f8eed594ac137a5f2484d8.poster.avif?t=1772214907\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392900/extras/eade8657f9f8eed594ac137a5f2484d8.webm?t=1772214907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392900/extras/eade8657f9f8eed594ac137a5f2484d8.mp4?t=1772214907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
